
<head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/main.css" />
    
    <!-- Title -->
    <title>Text based therapy</title>
    
    <!-- Script for function to show the statistics graph -->
    <script>
        function showImg() {
            var x = document.getElementById("toHide");
            x.style.display = "block"
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar to go to the section-->
    <nav class="navbar fixed-top navbar-expand-lg navbar-light fixed-top" id="top-navbar">
        <div id="navbarResponsive" class="collapse navbar-collapse">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="#about">About</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="#advantages">Advantages</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="#subscribe">Subscribe</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <!-- About section, includes the input field for age and button to show image -->
    <section id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 col-sm-12 col-12 col-md-12" id="about-text">
                    <br><br><br><br>
                    <!-- Shows the name based on the last subscriber's name -->
                    <h1 class="basic-info">HI <%=name %>, we welcome you to learn about text based therapy.</h1>
                    <br><br>
                    <h2 class="basic-info">Why choose text based therapy?</h2>
                    <br>
                    <p class="basic-info">Due to the current pandemic, people are searching for therapy and counseling online at a rate higher than ever.</p>
                    <br>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-7 col-sm-7 col-7 col-md-7" id="about-text">
                    <h2>Please enter your age to find out your mental health statistics.</h2>
                    <!-- Field to enter the age and submit a post request -->
                    <div>
                        <form action = "/check" method = "POST">
                            <label for = "age">Age</label>
                            <input type = "number" id = "age" name = "age" min = "0" max = "150" required>
                            <button type = "submit" >Check</button>
                        </form>
                        <!-- Displays the percentage text based on the input-->
                        <% if (percentage!=null) { %> 
                            <h2 id="result">The number of individuals in your age group that was affected by a mental health issue is <%=percentage %> percent.</h2>
                            <%} %> 
                        <!-- Button for the show image function-->
                        <button onclick="showImg()">Overall statistics</button>
                           
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Image that shows up after function is called -->
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-5 col-5 col-md-5" id="about-text">
                    <div id="toHide">
                        <img id="hiddenImg" src="images/Fig2-1.gif">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-12 col-sm-12 col-12 col-md-12" id="about-text">
                    <br><br>
                    <h2 class="basic-info">Here are the three main advantages of using text based therapy.</h2>
                    <br><br>
                </div>  
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Section with images that show text after hovering-->
    <section id="advantages">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <br><br><br><br>
                <h2 id ="importantmessage">Hover over the images to see the answer!</h2>
                <br><br><br><br>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 col-6 col-md-6" id="about-text">
                    <br><br><br><br>
                    <h2 class="basic-info">How can we reach out to the newer generation of teenage athelets?</h2>
                   
                </div> 
                <!-- Images that can be hovered over, details in css -->
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 col-6 col-md-6" id="hover">
                    <div class="hvrbox">
                        <img id="insideimages" src="images/image6.png" class="hvr-image">
                        <!-- Text that is displayed after hovering-->
                        <div class="hvrbox-top">
                            <p>Texting! Currently, the largest userbase of existing online therapy platforms and other social media platforms are teenagers.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div> 
                    <br><br><br><br>
                </div>       
            </div>
        </div>       
    </section>
    <!-- Same as above section with image on the left this time-->
    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 col-6 col-md-6" id="hover">
                    <div class="hvrbox">
                        <img id="insideimages" src="images/image1.png" class="hvr-image">
                        <div class="hvrbox-top">
                            <p>The answer is stigmas related to mental health. Athletes, particularly male athletes, are more worried about their physical and mental shape. Thus, the anonymous feature of text based therapy can help them overcome this fear of the stigma</p>
                        </div>
                    </div> 
                    <br><br><br><br>
                </div> 
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 col-6 col-md-6" id="about-text">
                    <br><br><br><br>
                    <h2 class="basic-info">Why has text therapy been so helpful to atheletes?</h2>
            
                </div> 
                <br><br><br><br>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </section>
    <!-- Same as first image hovering section with different text -->
    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 col-6 col-md-6" id="about-text">
                    <br><br><br><br>
                    <h2 class="basic-info">What is the largest barrier to seeking mental health care?</h2>
                 
                </div> 
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 col-6 col-md-6" id="hover">
                    <div class="hvrbox">
                        <img id="insideimages" src="images/image10.png" class="hvr-image">
                        <div class="hvrbox-top">
                            <p>Cost and time! With text based therapy, these barriers of health care are drastically reduced. Furthermore, text based therapy has been shown to be just as effective as in person therapy sessions.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div> 
                    <br><br><br><br>
                </div> 
                
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </section>
    <!-- Subscribe section with form and subscribe on left side, unsubscribe and download on the right side-->
    <section id="subscribe">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Left side -->
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-sm-8 col-8 col-md-8">
                    <!-- Creates post request for submitting the form -->
                    <form action = "/" method = "POST">
                        <h2>Subscribe!</h2>
                        <!-- Shows error or successful message -->
                        <% if (message.length > 0) { %> 
                        <div><%= message %> </div>
                        <%} %> 
                        <div>
                            <label for = "name">Name</label>
                            <input type = "text" id = "name" name = "name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label for = "email">Email</label>
                            <input type = "text" id = "email" name = "email" required>
                        </div>
                        <button type = "submit">Subscribe</button>
                    </form>
                </div> 
                <!-- Right side -->
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-4 col-4 col-md-4">
                    <br><br>
                    <!-- Two links, one to the unsubscribe page, one to the download request-->
                    <a id="finaltext" href = "/unsubscribe">Unsubscribe</a>
                    <br>
                    <a id="finaltext" href = "/download">Download</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </section>
    
    <!-- Option 1: jQuery and Bootstrap Bundle (includes Popper) -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ho+j7jyWK8fNQe+A12Hb8AhRq26LrZ/JpcUGGOn+Y7RsweNrtN/tE3MoK7ZeZDyx" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    
</body>

